  "\\label{rmk:deponbasepoint}\n  \\ref{def:fundgrp}\n  For a path $a : x \\to y$, define \n  \\[\n    \\gamma[a] : \\pi_1(X,x) \\to \\pi_1(X,y)\n  \\]\n\n  by \n  \\[\n    \\gamma[a][f] = [a \\cdot f \\cdot a^{-1}]\n  \\]\n\n  This is a homomorphism of groups.",
