  "\\label{def:kernel-image}\nFor a homomorphism $\\phi : G \\to H$ (Definition~\\ref{def:group-hom}), the \\emph{kernel} and \\emph{image} are\n\\[\n  \\ker \\phi := \\{ g \\in G \\mid \\phi(g) = e_H \\}, \\qquad\n  \\operatorname{im} \\phi := \\{ \\phi(g) \\mid g \\in G \\}.\n\\]",
  :type :definition,
  :title "Kernel and Image",
  :concepts [],
  :label "def:kernel-image",
