  "\\label{def:quotient-group}\nLet $N \\trianglelefteq G$ be a normal subgroup (Definition~\\ref{def:subgroup}).\nThe \\emph{quotient group} $G/N$ is the set of left cosets $\\{ gN \\mid g \\in G \\}$ equipped with the operation $(aN)(bN) := (ab)N$.",
