  "\\label{def:topological-space}\nA \\emph{topological space} is a pair $(X, \\mathcal{T})$ where $\\mathcal{T}$ is a collection of subsets of $X$ (the \\emph{open sets}) satisfying: $\\emptyset, X \\in \\mathcal{T}$; arbitrary unions of open sets are open; finite intersections of open sets are open.",
