  "\\label{def:simply-connected}\nA path-connected space $X$ (Definition~\\ref{def:connected}) is \\emph{simply connected} if every loop $\\gamma : [0,1] \\to X$ with $\\gamma(0) = \\gamma(1)$ can be continuously contracted to a point, i.e., the fundamental group $\\pi_1(X) = 0$.",
