  :latex
  "\\label{def:tangent-space}\nFor $p \\in M$ a smooth manifold (Definition~\\ref{def:smooth-manifold}), the \\emph{tangent space} $T_pM$ is the vector space of derivations on smooth functions near $p$. Concretely in a chart, it is spanned by $\\partial/\\partial x^i|_p$. The \\emph{tangent bundle} is $TM = \\bigsqcup_{p \\in M} T_pM$.",
  :type :definition,
  :title "Tangent Space",
  :concepts [],
  :label "def:tangent-space",
