  :latex
  "\\label{def:subrepresentation}\nGiven a $G$-representation $(V, \\rho)$ (Definition~\\ref{def:representation}), a subspace $W \\subseteq V$ is \\emph{$G$-invariant} (a \\emph{subrepresentation}) if $\\rho(g)w \\in W$ for all $g \\in G$, $w \\in W$.\nThe restriction $\\rho|_W$ then defines a representation of $G$ on $W$.",
  :type :definition,
  :title "Subrepresentation and Invariant Subspace",
  :concepts [],
  :label "def:subrepresentation",
  :id "45f1bf4d",
  :source-file "lie-groups.tex",
