  :latex
  "\\label{def:irreducible}\nA representation $(V, \\rho)$ (Definition~\\ref{def:representation}) is \\emph{irreducible} (or \\emph{simple}) if $V \\neq 0$ and its only subrepresentations (Definition~\\ref{def:subrepresentation}) are $\\{0\\}$ and $V$ itself.",
  :type :definition,
