  "\\label{def:direct-sum-rep}\nGiven $G$-representations $(V, \\rho)$ and $(W, \\sigma)$ (Definition~\\ref{def:representation}), their \\emph{direct sum} is $(V \\oplus W, \\rho \\oplus \\sigma)$ where $(\\rho \\oplus \\sigma)(g)(v, w) = (\\rho(g)v, \\sigma(g)w)$.",
