  "\\label{def:complete-reducibility}\nA representation $V$ (Definition~\\ref{def:representation}) is \\emph{completely reducible} (semisimple) if it decomposes as a direct sum (Definition~\\ref{def:direct-sum-rep}) of irreducible subrepresentations (Definition~\\ref{def:irreducible}, Definition~\\ref{def:subrepresentation}).",
