  "\\label{prop:character-iso}\nIsomorphic representations (Definition~\\ref{def:morphism-rep}) have equal characters (Definition~\\ref{def:character}).\nFor compact groups (Definition~\\ref{def:compact}), the converse holds: two representations are isomorphic if and only if their characters are equal.",
