  "\\label{def:lie-group}\n  A \\emph{Lie Group} is a group (Definition \\ref{def:group-classical}) that is also a finite dimensional smooth differentiable manifold (Definition \\ref{def:smooth-manifold}), with the added\n  condition that the group operations of multiplication and inversion are smooth maps (Definition \\ref{def:smooth-map}).",
  :type :definition,
